{"tid":1651903,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"香港戲院上映《此時此刻—國慶70週年盛典》全日所有場次合共只有8個觀眾","createTime":"2019-10-13T13:24:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T14:51:19.000Z","uid":41343,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"34175b0c1d957f84178fbfe831bc9880be27c852","tid":1651903,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:24:22.000Z","msg":"本周雖然共有六部電影於周四開畫，不過令人感到更為震撼的，便是由寰亞發行、中央廣播電視總台與央視頻出品的《此時此刻&mdash;國慶70週年盛典》在周五忽然在香港上映。而昨天雖然是周末時間，不過這部比《我和我的祖國》更加「愛國」的電影，似乎被香港觀眾所唾棄。<br />\n<br />\n《此時此刻&mdash;國慶70週年盛典》昨天安排於十一間戲院各映一場，全部場次均為中午前的早場，結果合共只錄到八位觀眾，每場平均連一個觀眾也沒有。<br />\n<br />\n不過，更令人感到吃驚的是，十一間上映的戲院當中，其中七間出現零入座入人次的「吉場」情況，包括了Festival Grand Cinema、嘉禾啟德、Grand Kornhill Cinema、K11 Art House、MCL粉嶺、UA東薈城與UA MegaBox。<br />\n<br />\n其餘四間錄得入座的戲院方面，數碼港百老匯與MCL德福戲院則錄得一名長者包場的狀況，將軍澳的MCL新都城則錄得一名長者與一名非長者觀眾。成績最佳要算是九龍站的Premiere Elements，合共錄得四位觀眾，當中包括三位長者與一名非長者。<br />\n<br />\n結果，十一場放映，七場「吉場」，而八名入場觀眾，當中六名便是長者，莫非是順道為自己來慶祝生日乎。如斯的成績，實在令人感到將這部電影在港發行，看來人為求上映便算居多。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/71606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkfilmblog.com%2Farchives%2F71606&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=9d93f17f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkfilmblog.com/archives/71606</a>"},{"pid":"c060ee706932fa7a1858575278420b02f3b85a2f","tid":1651903,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:25:40.000Z","msg":"唔派錢你叫人點愛國？"},{"pid":"b940e424ae5ee770f7ca11f2b86deef147a17c8a","tid":1651903,"uid":1241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:25:41.000Z","msg":"乜有呢套戲架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"492974439ec28dc2a89da9463d40f4edcd65ad66","tid":1651903,"uid":21139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b940e424ae5ee770f7ca11f2b86deef147a17c8a","tid":1651903,"uid":1241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:25:41.000Z","msg":"乜有呢套戲架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:27:19.000Z","msg":"仲冷清過《厲害了，我的國》<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bcef2aa3788380e7a03d0dd2384b57855e2f6b","tid":1651903,"uid":228337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:29:30.000Z","msg":"民賤聯同暴動先驅會組團車啲公公婆婆去睇㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366a5323d13a8ec7589cedc99f3a8bb0816581d6","tid":1651903,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:33:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8H2d3fN1bGE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8H2d3fN1bGE&d=uxh%2FksCcDU8UuFRsnlXnuT2nqaxvu5zgGSEBmbQkQbg%3D&h=15521601\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8H2d3fN1bGE</a>"},{"pid":"7a7ac9ed9488bd1369d93093b80abcc32958108c","tid":1651903,"uid":157588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:37:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6db6a4f21bd8a05c4a3ddf2cb7e2aef2c4468274","tid":1651903,"uid":171931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:41:20.000Z","msg":"區選進行中，冇得搞睇戲團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad48442dce76bead11b04c76db7356090d9d593e","tid":1651903,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:44:11.000Z","msg":"真心佩服嗰八位觀眾, 定係當左帶位都係"},{"pid":"79e84cc140ce94cb16e9e9011eeb63c95ed46391","tid":1651903,"uid":94516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad48442dce76bead11b04c76db7356090d9d593e","tid":1651903,"uid":289751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T13:44:11.000Z","msg":"真心佩服嗰八位觀眾, 定係當左帶位都係"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T14:37:03.000Z","ms